## Game-Specific Components

### QuestionCard
- Display question text prominently (large, bold)
- Show question number and total
- Category badge with icon
- Timer indicator if timed

### AnswerButton
- Large touch target (min 56px height)
- Clear selected/unselected states
- Correct/incorrect feedback animations
- Disabled state after answering

### ScoreDisplay
- Animated number counter
- Star/trophy icons
- Progress toward next level

### ProgressBar
- Visual progress (not just numbers)
- Current question indicator
- Celebratory animation on completion

### Timer
- Circular or linear progress
- Color changes as time runs out
- Pulse animation in last seconds

